/**
 * Recommended profile for projects targeting the [XSMP-SDK](https://github.com/ThalesGroup/xsmp-sdk).
 *
 * It configures the XSMP SDK-oriented project layout and generation workflow used to build and test SMP simulators with XSMP Modeler.
 *
 * Documentation:
 * - [XSMP-SDK User Guide](https://thalesgroup.github.io/xsmp-sdk/)
 * - [XSMP-SDK Repository](https://github.com/ThalesGroup/xsmp-sdk)
 */
profile 'xsmp-sdk'
